abstract: >-
  Ten standalone prompt briefs for downstream Claude Code Opus 4.7 sessions to
  author Physical AI oncology clinical trial demonstrations. Each demo focuses
  on humanoid robotic agents (Atlas, Optimus, Figure, Digit, Apollo, Phoenix,
  Neo, H2) coordinated by on-premise large language models performing surgical
  and patient care tasks inside clinical trial sites and for pharmaceutical
  company sponsors. Companion repository to physical-ai-oncology-trials.
